name: 109-23 71st Rd Queens, NY 11375

The ideal location in Forest Hills; the 71st Avenue subway station (E,F,R,M) service is located just around the corner for swift and reliable commuting to midtown. Take advantage of all the shopping and entertainment immediately available along acclaimed Austin Street, just across Queens Boulevard. LIRR service is also available. Conveniently located for both LaGuardia and Kennedy airports. Call today to schedule a viewing. Sponsor unit, no board approval necessary.
